    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Through long and intensive training you mastered Operative. Few people in this world can match your capabilities in this area.</p><p>Gain the following master feats: choose one of @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.IJQJBnD5CjKvFYEx]{Foil Senses}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Imvu2RV2ggjJ2HZt]{Swift Sneak}.</p><p><strong>Skill Potency</strong></p><p>At 9th level, you gain a +2 item bonus to Stealth checks involving @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.IE2nThCmoyhQA0Jn]{Avoid Notice}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.qVNVSmsgpKFGk9hV]{Conceal an Object}. At 17th level, if you have @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.n0urrOL8YlnVBVRQ]{Legendary Sneak}, this bonus increases to +3.</p>",
